  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overcoming all odds and heading towards the Hurricane</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/7e2c9e4d896299bbddf6c08fd5b90e02.poster.avif?t=1669573327\" width=512 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/7e2c9e4d896299bbddf6c08fd5b90e02.webm?t=1669573327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/7e2c9e4d896299bbddf6c08fd5b90e02.mp4?t=1669573327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>CubeCube is an animated 3D Roguelite game. Every failure will start over again. <br>The ancient land was covered by water, CubeCube has to make a decision for the sealed creature. Beat whoever stand against CubeCube, build your own combat style. Discover the ancient relic and head to the Hurricane.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/f2c439523c560d92f0813a08137110eb.poster.avif?t=1669573327\" width=512 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/f2c439523c560d92f0813a08137110eb.webm?t=1669573327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/f2c439523c560d92f0813a08137110eb.mp4?t=1669573327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feature of CubeCube</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tightly combat, make decision between rolling and attack, catch opportunity, beat enemy!<br></li><li>Upgrade unceasingly, build your own combat style. <br></li><li>Fails is a new begin.<br></li><li>CubeCube can recall and transform to each characters who has been defeated by CubeCube.<br></li><li>Some of level will spawn randomly<br></li><li>CubeCube can customize the attack action sequence</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/72de78ba7209b79051524fa470e3c2b9.poster.avif?t=1669573327\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/72de78ba7209b79051524fa470e3c2b9.webm?t=1669573327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/72de78ba7209b79051524fa470e3c2b9.mp4?t=1669573327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/1f382f2aab1d2fe98080bc86f3eb42d0.poster.avif?t=1669573327\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/1f382f2aab1d2fe98080bc86f3eb42d0.webm?t=1669573327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/1f382f2aab1d2fe98080bc86f3eb42d0.mp4?t=1669573327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/074c882cdb475c916a6b34eeff85c2fe.poster.avif?t=1669573327\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/074c882cdb475c916a6b34eeff85c2fe.webm?t=1669573327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/074c882cdb475c916a6b34eeff85c2fe.mp4?t=1669573327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
