 by CubeCube.<br></li><li>Some of level will spawn randomly<br></li><li>CubeCube can customize the attack action sequence</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/72de78ba7209b79051524fa470e3c2b9.poster.avif?t=1669573327\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/72de78ba7209b79051524fa470e3c2b9.webm?t=1669573327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/72de78ba7209b79051524fa470e3c2b9.mp4?t=1669573327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/1f382f2aab1d2fe98080bc86f3eb42d0.poster.avif?t=1669573327\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/1f382f2aab1d2fe98080bc86f3eb42d0.webm?t=1669573327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/1f382f2aab1d2fe98080bc86f3eb42d0.mp4?t=1669573327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/074c882cdb475c916a6b34eeff85c2fe.poster.avif?t=1669573327\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/074c882cdb475c916a6b34eeff85c2fe.webm?t=1669573327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1677650/extras/074c882cdb475c916a6b34eeff85c2fe.mp4?t=1669573327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>